This project is a Karpathy-style LLM Wiki.

Core files:
- `AGENTS.md`: canonical wiki schema and operating contract.
- `manifest.md`: ingestion control plane.
- `raw/`: immutable source documents.
- `wiki/index.md`: first page to read when querying the wiki.
- `wiki/log.md`: chronological activity log.

Keep this rule short. Put detailed workflows in `AGENTS.md` and task-specific rules.
